[{"Id": 1014874, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Quoted from Kafi too, the Holy Prophet (s) is reported to have said, “Whoever recites the verses of Surah <Baqarah (2:1-4)>, <Aayatul Kursi> and the verses of Surah <Baqarah (2:284-286)>, will not experience any misfortune in himself and in his property; will not be contacted by Satan; and will not forget the Holy Qur’an.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Al Kafi mein Hazrat Rasool-e-Khuda (s) se manqool ha keh “Agar koi shakhs Surah <Baqarah (2:1-4)>, <Aayatul Kursi> aur Surah <Baqarah (2:284-286)> aayato’n ki tilaawat karega to apni jaan o maal mein aisi koi baat nahi dekhega jo usey na-gawar guzre, Shaitaan uske qareeb nahi phatkega aur na Qur’an ko woh faramosh karega.", "UrduDescription": "شیخ کلینیؒ کی کافی میں ہے کہ رسول اﷲؐنے فرمایا: جو شخص سورہ <بقرہ: ۱۔۴> آیات، <آیت الکرسی> اور سورہ <بقرہ: ۲۸۴۔۲۸۶> آیات کی تلاوت کیا کرے تو وہ اپنی جان و مال میں ایسی کوئی بات نہیں دیکھے گا جو اسے ناگوار گزرے شیطان اس کے قریب نہ آئے گا اور نہ قرآن کو فراموش کرے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null